<plot>Len Howard has been sent to protect a large gold shipment that is on a train traveling from Albuquerque to Tombstone. First he passes out guns so the passengers can fight off an Indian attack. Then when a gang dressed as Indians attack, he helps fight them off and identifies their leader who is one of the passengers.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?615623</url></doc>
